{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/steamClipA_low.gif?t=1733728427\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Become The Alchemist</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock your true potential as you ascend! Obtain the ability to grab your enemies and absorb their powers! Boost your magic by with the Philiosopher's Stone, a terrible artifact that breathes life into inanimate objects! Use spells to summon an army of ghosts, meteor-strikes, swirling chain-saws and lots more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/steamsiteGrabs.gif?t=1733728427\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Tower Never Ends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rise to the Assembly and face off against the Laser Sharks! Find yourself in the darkness of the Catacombs, lair of the elusive Valchemist! Fight invaders amongst the stars as you ascend toward your ultimate opponent - the Immortal Samurai! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/steamClipC.gif?t=1733728427\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Several Modes To Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Classic Mode:</u> Unlock new permanent abilites throughout the game, which you can use in other modes such as Time Attack or Survival Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>REMIX Mode:</u> A hardcore way to play the game - only a handful of power-ups are available as you dash through the tower at a rapid pace! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Survival Mode:</u> Fight against the clock. Enemies will amass in even greater<br>numbers than before, and bosses appear of their own volition while you scramble to survive for as long as you can. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/steamsiteMonsters.gif?t=1733728427\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the fantastical world of a music artist like never before in Savant - Ascent </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">REMIX, now on Windows &amp; Mac! Like the game and looking to connect with the devs &amp; it's fans! Join our Discord today (link in side-panel)! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/banner.png?t=1733728427\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Rise Up!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2279330/559cb314d34a9545cf64d067646ad38039b99e56.jpg"},{"name":"Hit The Top","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2279330/bb6f0c272673d99d69afbc2635bf016a039d8db1.jpg"},{"name":"Vario Time!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2279330/80bfebd4e23c4c58052b08291e5d4f13a594211d.jpg"},{"name":"Smells fishy!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2279330/690f452a721c0911a0a9456f9de2382ce5224451.jpg"},{"name":"Lasers Aren't Enough!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2279330/ad6b1375fd8e633db54cc4fbdc09251f54c72ab9.jpg"},{"name":"Dancer In The Dark","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2279330/bf533cbf5c262053abf3c353051589d9f4c20b50.jpg"},{"name":"Into The Void.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2279330/78f29227adfe89e10fc324162620420a781197d5.jpg"},{"name":"Sky Is The Limit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2279330/3de66f0d35c3e4cdc00d65b8f59f9a4574d36497.jpg"},{"name":"Sayonara","p